Sends an [HTTP DELETE](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Methods/DELETE) request to the
specified URL. See [http.delete()](atlas/app-services/services/http-actions/http.delete) for detailed reference
information, including parameter definitions and return types.

```javascript
exports = async function() {
   const response = await context.http.delete({ url: "https://www.example.com/user/8675309" })
};
```

